<p>All three 2c/5 spaceships, and the c/6 spaceship, can be <a href= 
"guns.html">shot from guns</a>.  Many higher-period c/2 spaceships
can be made using
<a href="puffer.html">Jason Summers' puffer constructions</a>.</p>

